JxBot Install
=============

! IMPORTANT:  This software is an advanced state of DEVELOPMENT - and is not ready 
for production use on public web servers.  Use at your own risk!


1.  Upload the JxBot directory to an appropriate location on your web server.

2.	Create a MySQL database.

3.  Point your web browser at the JxBot directory, eg.

	http://localhost/jxbot/
	
4.	Follow the instructions in the Installer.

5.	Configure your bot further and upload AIML in the administration interface.

6.	'Activate' your bot in the System Settings of the administration interface.

7.	Happy chatting!
